    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline, benefiting from a recent VANOS service and rod bearing replacement for long-term engine health. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been proactively addressed with subframe reinforcement plates, and the suspension maintains excellent damping characteristics with refreshed bushings. While showing honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver\u2019s car, the drivetrain and cooling system are in peak operational state. A purposeful, high-performance machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 31500.0,
