      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and refined performance. The exterior retains a beautiful shine, showing only the expected minor touches of road wear that come with regular use. Step inside to a spacious, well-preserved interior featuring premium upholstery that remains firm and comfortable, complemented by a pristine dashboard and intuitive tech features that all function as intended. Under the hood, the car has been treated to a rigorous maintenance schedule; it starts reliably, idles smoothly, and handles with precision. We recently completed a full fluid flush and a comprehensive safety inspection, so it is truly turn-key and ready for its next owner. This car offers a smooth, quiet ride and has been kept in a smoke-free environment. It comes complete with a full service log and a clean title.",
